Find the value of x in the proportion. Check the answer.

  12 / (x + 2) = 6 / 7

x........................
12 / (x + 2) = 6 / 7
12(7) = 6(x + 2)
84 = 6x + 12
72 = 6x
12 = x

Check x (proportion).....
12 / (x + 2) = 6 / 7
12 / (12 + 2) = 6 / 7
12 / 14 = 6 / 7
6 / 7 = 6 / 7

Check x (cross product)..
12 / 14 = 6 / 7
12(7) = 14(6)
84 = 84

