A top fuel dragster can use as much as 6 gallons in 4.5 seconds to travel
1/4 miles. At this rate, how many gallons of fuel will it take for the
dragster to go 1 mile?


gallons / miles = gallons / miles

g...................
6 / (1/4) = g / 1
6(1) = (1/4)(g)
6 = g / 4
24 = g

